With help from COEs across the floor:

1. Downloading the policies manually:
-------------------------------------

-> kinit before running the below command:

$ curl -iv -k --negotiate -u : -H "Content-type:application/json" -X GET http://<HOST>:<PORT>/service/plugins/policies/download/<repository_name>

$ curl "https://<ranger_hots>:6182/service/plugins/secure/policies/download/<reponame>" -k
